==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: North-Central
<hw>North-Central</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to a region
of the U. S. generally including states of the upper Mississippi valley
and Great Lakes region lying north of the Ohio River and the southern
boundaries of Kansas and Missouri and between the western boundary of
Pennsylvania and the eastern boundaries of Montana; Wyoming; and
Colorado.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

